@node 7

@{b}                                  TOOLTYPES@{ub}
                                 ===========

The following entries in the SchematiCAD.info icon tooltypes may be set.

Name:           Set:    Default if not set:

FONT *          PEARL   Or if font cannot be found - TOPAZ.
MEMWARN                 100000 (bytes)
PRTWIDTH        2000    1000
PRTHEIGHT       2000    1000
F_RATE		3500	3500

F_RATE determines the "Flash Rate" when pasting from the clipboard.

* FONT does not need ".font" suffix

@endnode
